{"tid":2000881,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump : 中國「犯了一個可怕的錯誤，但不想承認」 ，遲遲不讓美國專家和世衛專家入境。","createTime":"2020-05-04T07:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T16:56:13.000Z","uid":249945,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"232f59688c57d47f2ef814c4bb81fce8a8921d45","tid":2000881,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:01:46.000Z","msg":"特朗普表示，他認為在疫情爆發問題上，中國「犯了一個可怕的錯誤，但不想承認」，（I think they made a horrible mistake and didn&rsquo;t want to admit it），遲遲不讓美國專家和世衛專家入境。他說，「我的看法是他們犯了一個錯誤。他們試圖掩蓋，試圖撲熄。就像着了火一樣。你知道，這就好像是要把火撲熄。他們沒辦法把火撲熄。」（My opinion is they made a mistake. They tried to cover it, they tried to put it out. It&rsquo;s like a fire.You know, it&rsquo;s really like trying to put out a fire. They couldn&rsquo;t put out the fire）。<br />\n<br />\n當被問到是否認為有足夠證據證明，中國在疫情上誤導國際社會。特朗普稱，他不認為這有任何疑問，重申他對北京試圖將問題歸咎美軍感到「非常憤怒」。至於武漢肺炎是否是從武漢一間實驗室泄漏的問題，他說政府將完成一份結論性很強的（very conclusive）報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/29527/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82-%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-29527/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%8C%E7%B5%82%E6%A5%B5%E6%87%B2%E7%BD%B0%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F29527%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582-%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585-29527%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%2587%25B2%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E3%2580%258D&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=e36147aa\" data-auto-link target=\